#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To book an lesson, learner would first have to buy some lessons to have pre-"
"paid lessons on their loyalty cards. Then they can reach the website and "
"click the Schedule an appointment button."
msgstr ""
"ໃນການຈອງບົດຮຽນ, ນັກຮຽນຕ້ອງຊື້ບົດຮຽນກ່ອນ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ມີຍອດບົດຮຽນໃນບັດສະສົມຄະແນນ. ຫຼັງຈາກນັ້ນ ເຂົາເຈົ້າສ"
"າມາດເຂົ້າເວັບໄຊ ແລະ ຄລິກປຸ່ມ \"ນັດໝາຍເວລາ\"."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To help you planning lessons without the hurdle of assigning slots to "
"learners, <strong>Appointments App </strong>will expose self bookable "
"appointments."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍທ່ານວາງແຜນບົດຮຽນໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງຫຍຸ້ງຍາກໃນການມອບໝາຍເວລາໃຫ້ນັກຮຽນ, <strong>ແອັບການນັດໝາ"
"ຍ</strong> ຈະສະແດງຊ່ວງເວລາທີ່ນັກຮຽນສາມາດຈອງໄດ້ດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To help you planning lessons without the hurdle of assigning slots to "
"learners, Appointments App will expose self bookable appointments. Let's see"
" how instructors can use <strong>Calendar App </strong>then to know their "
"planning."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍທ່ານວາງແຜນບົດຮຽນໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງມອບໝາຍເວລາດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ, ແອັບການນັດໝາຍຈະສະແດງຊ່ວງເວລາໃຫ້ຈອງ"
"ໄດ້. ລອງມາເບິ່ງວ່າຄູຝຶກຈະໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບປະຕິທິນ</strong> ເພື່ອເບິ່ງແຜນວຽກຂອງເຂົາເຈົ້າໄດ້ແນວໃດ."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To manage waivers, we take advantage of the <strong>Sign App </strong>from "
"the customer form."
msgstr ""
"ໃນການຈັດການເອກະສານສະລະສິດ, ພວກເຮົາໃຊ້ປະໂຫຍດຈາກ <strong>ແອັບການເຊັນ</strong> ໂດຍກົງຈາ"
"ກຟອມຂໍ້ມູນລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: driving_school
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:driving_school.homepage
msgid ""
"Transform your driving skills with<br/>our lessons. Contact us<br/>to start "
"your journey!<br/>"
msgstr ""
"ພັດທະນາທັກສະການຂັບຂີ່ຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍ<br/>ບົດຮຽນຂອງພວກເຮົາ. ຕິດຕໍ່ຫາພວກເຮົາ<br/>ເພື່ອເລີ່ມຕົ້ນການຮຽນ"
"ຮູ້!<br/>"

#. module: driving_school
